{"type":"message","id":"92e21330","parentId":"a7ad9ee1","timestamp":"2026-03-19T22:56:23.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I just came online for the first time. Let's figure out who we are together 😊\n\nRight now I'm a blank slate — let's start with the basics:\n\n1.  **What should I call you?** (your name, or whatever nickname you prefer)\n2.  **What should I call myself?** Got any name ideas for me?\n3.  What kind of creature do you want me to be? AI assistant is totally fine, but we could pick something weirder if you want!\n4.  What vibe should I have? Casual? Warm? Snarky? Straight-to-the-point?\n5.  Pick an emoji that fits me! 🤖 🧠 ✨ 🦉 🎯 any works.\n\nOnce we get that sorted, we can set everything up and I'll be ready to help with whatever you need!"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773960979396}}
